message.body: Hey Michelle can I get the Getty image ASAP? I have to bring them somewhere to be printed and have to do it during business hours. Thanks
We haven't gotten to it and still needs to be approved by the agency, so I think we'll have to print it ourselves today
Ok I'll go buy some photo paper for my printer, let me know if anything changes and I'll have it professionally printed
Ok we may do kinkos if we don't get it to you in time
Is wardrobe renting or bringing a steamer? It'd be great to have on hand for the backdrops too
